commitMessage:
Bug 569845 - [AutoRefactor immigration #50/146] [cleanup & saveaction]
Unreachable block

Detects two if conditions that are identical and removes the second one:
- The conditions should be passive,
- No exceptions should be awaited,
- It should not create unreachable code below the if statement, that is
to say the case where only the removed block doesn't fall through, all
the other cases fall through, there is an else and a code is below.

Given:
if (b1 && b2) {
    return 0;
} else if (b2 && b1) {
    return 1;
}

When:
Clean up the code enabling "Unreachable block"

Then:
if (b1 && b2) {
    return 0;
}

Change-Id: I186720e12386800386f3f861f51e4ff1be7b30ee
Signed-off-by: Fabrice Tiercelin <fabrice.tiercelin@yahoo.fr>

